  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      Study to determine if pulmonary/critical care fellows will demonstrate increased competency
      in the behavioral skills necessary to facilitate family meetings focused on discussions of
      goals of care in the ICU from pre- to post-communication skills training.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
  <detailed_description>
    <textblock>
      The investigators hypothesize that pulmonary/critical care fellows will demonstrate increased
      competency in the behavioral skills necessary to facilitate family meetings focused on
      discussions of goals of care in the ICU from pre- to post-communication skills training.
    </textblock>
  </detailed_description>
